==================================================
ledmatrix7219d88 lib
==================================================
= Copyright (c) Davide Gironi, 2013              =
= http://davidegironi.blogspot.it/               =
==================================================


This library implements a 8x8 led matrix for AVR Atmega.
It uses just one MAX7219 serial input/output common-cathode display drivers
and 3 micro ports.
MAX7219 can refresh leds leving more resources to microcontroller.
This library uses MAX7219 without the need of SPI. User can setup scan limit
and intensity setup.
Multiple led matrix can be attached.

Setup parameters are stored in file ledmatrix7219d88.h


Devel Notes
-----------
This library was developed on Eclipse, built with avr-gcc on Atmega8 @ 1MHz.


